{#
name: Event Handler
description: Handle events by type with configurable handlers and filters
tags: [workflow, event, handler]
parameters:
  - name: skill_name
    type: str
    description: Skill display name
    required: true
  - name: skill_description
    type: str
    description: Brief description of event handling purpose
    required: true
  - name: event_types
    type: str
    description: Comma-separated event types to handle (e.g. create,update,delete)
    required: true
  - name: handlers
    type: str
    description: Comma-separated handler names or actions per event type
    required: true
  - name: filters
    type: str
    description: Optional filter conditions (e.g. "status=active")
    default: ""
examples:
  - "Handle order events: create->notify, update->sync"
#}
---
name: {{ skill_name | kebab_case }}
description: {{ skill_description }}
metadata:
  author: owlclaw
  version: "1.0"
owlclaw:
  spec_version: "1.0"
  task_type: workflow
---
# {{ skill_name }} — 使用指南

## 目标

{{ skill_description }}

## 事件配置

- 事件类型：{{ event_types }}
- 处理器：{{ handlers }}
- 过滤条件：{{ filters }}

## 处理逻辑

1. 接收事件，按 event_types 路由
2. 应用 filters 过滤
3. 调用对应 handlers 执行

## 注意事项

- event_types 与 handlers 需一一对应
- filters 为空表示不过滤
